==English==
===Adjective===
'''undead''' (no comparative or superlative)

# Pertaining to a [[corpse]], though having qualities of [[life]].
# ([[horror]] [[fiction]]) Being [[animate]], though non-living.

===Noun===
'''undead''' (''uncountable'')

# ''Usually preceded by "the"'' Those [[creature]] which are [[dead]] yet [[still]] [[moving]].
#: ''In the [[zombie]] movie, an army of the undead [[accost]]ed some [[nubile]] [[skinny-dip]]ping [[teenager]]s.''

